Basic Terminal Commands

ctrl+shift+	-->	size up
ctrl-		-->	size down
ctrl+A  	--> 	start line
ctrl+E  	--> 	end line
ctrl+w		-->	one word delete
ctrl+U		-->	full line delete
ctrl+C          -->     interupt

su              -->     switch user root to current directory
su -            -->     switch user root to /root directory
cd              -->     change directory        --> .. for back to parent directory
cd ~            -->     takes to home directory
pwd             -->     print working directory
ls              -->     list all files          --> ls -lti, ltr, lta, ll

